\",\"reason\":\"The artifact contains classes such as WebdavRequestImpl, WebdavResponseImpl, DavServletRequest/Response, InputContextImpl, OutputContextImpl, and AbstractWebdavServlet that reference javax.servlet types; servlet-api is a provided dependency and is not pulled transitively for tests.\"}],\"agent_guidance\":\"No Docker service or special environment/system property appears necessary. Prefer in-memory/unit-style coverage of WebDAV XML, client methods, locator/request/response wrappers, and servlet-facing classes using mocks or simple test doubles rather than requiring a live WebDAV server.\",\"risks\":[\"The library is old and uses legacy servlet and commons-httpclient APIs; generated tests may need version-compatible mocks/test doubles rather than modern Jakarta Servlet types.\",\"SLF4J binding is not required for compile-time coverage, but tests may emit logging warnings if no test runtime binding is present.\"]}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_064d0931589c7eba016a4282326da4819487ff29bb047f4be0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1069, "output": 788, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34625, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782743588206, "responseId": "resp_064d0931589c7eba016a428224ef388194bfeece1fd7d4c90d"}}
